# ICON AMIP setup: experiment for JSBACH/VDIFF with NWP physics atmosphere
# based on runscript un_R2B4_G043_sml_002 by Ulrike Niemeier
#
# ------------------------------------------
# Copyright (C) 2004-2025, DWD, MPI-M, DKRZ, KIT, ETH, MeteoSwiss
# Contact information: icon-model.org
